{"tid":108844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5萬套中國製愛滋檢測工具充公　墨西哥指顯示假陰性結果","createTime":"2017-02-05T14:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T03:00:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad188190026311d8461b7fad28a28b930fa477b6","tid":108844,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"5萬套中國製愛滋檢測工具充公　墨西哥指顯示假陰性結果 (16:18)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170202/s00005/1486021576939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170202%2Fs00005%2F1486021576939&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m657TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b6c30fd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170202%2Fs00005%2F1486021576939&h=bf662e05\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170202/s00005/1486021576939</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170202/s00005/1486023464370SL4_10E561ACCCDD4F8DD5EB3A39A9ECB3B8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170202%2Fs00005%2F1486023464370SL4_10E561ACCCDD4F8DD5EB3A39A9ECB3B8.jpg&h=72a03be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墨西哥政府充公近4.7萬套中國製愛滋檢測工具，指工具可能會顯示假陰性結果。<br />\n<br />\n監管政府醫療事務的機構表示，有關工具原儲存在墨西哥灣沿岸維拉克魯斯州（Veracruz）一個政府醫用倉庫。機構指即使已感染愛滋病毒的人使用該工具進行測試，亦可能得出沒有感染病毒的假陰性結果，「令病人因此沒有接受治療，危害他們的性命」。<br />\n<br />\n維拉克魯斯州上任政府早前已被指涉嫌向州立醫院提供假藥物，現任政府指曾有癌症病童被注入沒有藥效的物質而非抗癌藥。<br />\n<br />\n（加拿大CTV News）"},{"pid":"bb9c6089a45ba43a8f471dcf18df14ae58b7b13e","tid":108844,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede3d0d4cc72d74c57a937dfcaad87eb76145b64","tid":1